Dear user,
To verify your Raiinmaker account, please follow these steps:

1. Open the Raiinmaker app and click on the three-dot button to open the profile menu.
2. Click on "Account Settings" and then select the "Security" option.
3. Click on "KYC Document Verification" and upload your data.
4. Follow the instructions carefully and ensure that you provide accurate information.
5. Once you have provided all necessary information, submit your KYC application for verification and approval.

You will receive a confirmation email from us within 72 hours, stating whether your application has been approved or rejected. Please note that it is important to provide correct information to ensure a smooth verification process.
